{"tid":1196033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實有冇人講過開始衝之後既出入策略係點？","createTime":"2019-06-09T17:37:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T23:24:37.000Z","uid":185121,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2fed82c057a0cd4de5594abe2faad98cbf02624f","tid":1196033,"uid":185121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T17:37:05.000Z","msg":"返完出嚟既其實可以點再入返去？<br />\n真係需要走既人點安全離開？<br />\n抗爭既持久力始終好需要其他人既接力同幫助運送資源，我相信有好多人雖然衝唔到係頭，但係其實依然有能力幫手做呢啲嘢。<br />\n<br />\n其實有冇呢啲既資訊比大眾知？定係其實有我睇唔到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：雖然我真係冇辦法直接衝出嚟，但我都想睇吓自己有冇其他嘢可以做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77f7d6df8b800932c5825a7f3a270baa562ec627","tid":1196033,"uid":185121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T17:51:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> hello , 有冇人見到"},{"pid":"daff17f989d5f82f92007f8b0adafa1bee0e93ed","tid":1196033,"uid":224095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T17:55:32.000Z","msg":"連登仔：Plan你老母，流動佔領呀，比警察捉得一個得一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69dae003c38ccc70fce712400df267bbf8c9a8db","tid":1196033,"uid":185121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T17:58:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又唔好咁講 始終呢啲嘢其實香港人經驗真心唔多  我哋真係需要更多既資源先有能力plan 更好既"},{"pid":"bbf70e86685db3ba3fae4653d2e2fbcaafb3e6c8","tid":1196033,"uid":185121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69dae003c38ccc70fce712400df267bbf8c9a8db","tid":1196033,"uid":185121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T17:58:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又唔好咁講 始終呢啲嘢其實香港人經驗真心唔多  我哋真係需要更多既資源先有能力plan 更好既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T17:58:25.000Z","msg":"係資料先啱"},{"pid":"6fe5da807d9dc2d1ab7330063808fb0d1e317ec3","tid":11960